      "value": "<p>The arcanist can select a metamagic feat as a bonus feat. She must meet the prerequisites of this feat. Each morning, when she prepares her spells, the arcanist can expend 1 point from her arcane reservoir to exchange this bonus feat for another metamagic feat, as long as she meets the prerequisites of the new feat.</p>\n<p>The arcanist must have the metamagic knowledge exploit to select this exploit.</p>",
